summary: Rids of ugly trees in the way of Lakeview, requires Hearthfire
descriptionHtml:
Rids of ugly trees in the way of Lakeview, requires Hearthfire

Made with [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28515]Lakeview Pool and Hot Bath for Hearthfire [/url] in mind.

Most of the trees on the left side of the lake viewing from the manor have been ridden of. I am thinking about defoliating the right side to make it easier to see the bridge, but it might make it seem too barren.

How to install:
Extract zip file into TESV.exe directory or install using NMM.
author: Bluezone
